snippet.title: Baby John And The Rescue Squad + More Little Angel Kids Songs & Nursery Rhymes
snippet.description:
Baby John and his rescue squad learn how to work together! They pretend play as police officers, firefighters and more to help those in need and have fun while doing so. Watch as the family work together to save the day! #littleangel #littleangelnurseryrhymes #babyjohnsongs 

(🔔) Subscribe to Little Angel for New Videos ►► http://bit.ly/Subscribe_to_LittleAngel

List of Kids Songs

00:00 Rescue Squad Is Here
03:38 Doctor Checkup
07:36 Parents Career Day
11:14 I Keep Everyone Safe
15:48 Baby John Wants to Be an Astronaut
19:36 Yes Yes You Can Do It
23:21 Wheres My Favourite Toy
27:06 Yes Yes Playground is Fun
31:09 Going to Fair

Song Lyrics

We are the Rescue Team
I help you 
You help me, cause
We’re better as a team
Look at how fast we go

Work together
Play together
We are the Rescue Team
You and you and me!

We are firefighters
Watch us go go go
Help me with the fire
Spray your water hose

Yeah!

Splash, splash the water goes
Out, out the fire goes
Rescue team saves the day!

We are the Rescue Team
I help you
You help me, cause
We’re better as a team
Look at how fast we go

Work together
Play together
We are the Rescue Team
You and you and me!

We are crime fighters!
Fighting crime today
Help me chase the bad guys!
They can’t get away

Yeah!
Vroom, vroom, the police car goes
Stop, stop, the bad guy goes
Rescue team saves the day!

We are the Rescue Team
I help you
You help me, cause
We’re better as a team
Look at how fast we go

Work together
Play together
We are the Rescue Team
You and you and me!

We are paramedics
Looking after you
Help me fix the boo boo
We need a band-aid too!

Yeah!
Check, check, that you’re okay
Fix, fix, you up and say
Rescue team saves the day!

We are the Rescue Team
I help you
You help me, cause
We’re better as a team
Look at how fast we go

Work together
Play together
We are the Rescue Team
You and you and me!
